<parameter name="content" string="true"># Fix Plan: Booking & Transaction Display Issues

## Root Causes Identified
- **Transactions "N/A"**: `wallet/serializers.py` catches all exceptions silently and returns "N/A" for non-booking transactions
- **Bookings not showing**: `bookings/permissions.py` case-sensitive role check, `bookings/serializers.py` lacks defensive guards

## Steps

### Step 1 ⬜ Fix `wallet/serializers.py`
- Fix `get_apartment_name`: return `None` (not "N/A") when no booking linked, log real errors
- Fix `get_unit_number`: handle missing booking gracefully
- Fix `get_booking_confirmation_code`: handle missing booking gracefully

### Step 2 ⬜ Fix `bookings/serializers.py`
- Add defensive try/except wrappers around all `SerializerMethodField` methods
- Add logging for actual errors

### Step 3 ⬜ Fix `bookings/permissions.py`
- Log denied requests with role info for debugging
- Add case-insensitive role check fallback
